Often no search query generates any results." Agriculture in Rowghun In Turkmenistan Fortas Zakhira, an English Language Programme teacher at Saparmura University and translator at EUTP, states, "In 2002, Russia agreed to have wheat shipped from Turkmenistan to be used in the production of bread in Siberia, in return for oil. However, in a few years time it was found that there was enough wheat already growing in Siberia.Thankfully, the dialogue was closed suddenly and so traders could not lose money by opening stores here." As was stated in a previous message, it is worth mentioning again, Turkmenistan is proud that Gurbansoltane Median, the sister of the 3rd and 4th Islamic Caliph, is from here.
